ary-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-fontweight:400;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-lineheight:120%;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-letterspacing:-0.4px"><span style="width:100%"><h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1></span></div><div data-rid="a2603559-0596-4d34-8cb6-0585f4349a89" class="r-hcqu01" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="c4793df1-c86f-4802-9302-f9dc4c87c737" class="r-1rivhq9" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="b94478b3-cef7-4319-af9a-060962e3ec9b" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R3b32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-9y7jff"><div data-rid="ab754200-9282-4d4e-a06c-4b158e7b2688" class="r-1jmjrvq alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>How fast will I feel Rejuvia working?</p></span></div><div data-rid="0287a8c3-7273-4b69-bd71-34627d5dc192" class="r-1602eum" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1qj68uv" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R3b32:"><div data-rid="ae80324b-e03e-4af7-a88e-df456d0cf6b4" class="r-18xvj6y"><div data-rid="446017e1-1cff-4419-8904-ad8e01b3c947" class="r-1jqcr4s alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Most people feel it the first or second night. Because the spray absorbs under your tongue, it skips your stomach completely and gets to work in about 10-15 minutes instead of the 60-90 minutes pills and gummies take. That said, if you've been dealing with bad sleep for years, give it a full 7-10 nights of consistent use. The ingredients build on each other and the deeper, full-night sleep typically kicks in by the end of week one.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="c399c433-228f-43bc-bdb0-c790c69c7a70" class="r-15qycdh" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="e9d7d3bb-fbfa-4665-bbfa-5f533266516c" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R5b32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1m2vq0q"><div data-rid="d97d5e76-9c75-4178-b276-a1a15fc4d3c5" class="r-xwiiph alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Will I wake up groggy in the morning?</p></span></div><div data-rid="b76fa3e7-6542-40f6-b305-9f45596ddba4" class="r-copzpz" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-zsfi3y" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R5b32:"><div data-rid="39fa9221-10f3-4783-8a7a-ccd57f1a3031" class="r-x6twal"><div data-rid="91510d5f-fd21-47dd-9632-dcd65c4ea0aa" class="r-1hgo9qf alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>No, and this is the #1 reason people switch to Rejuvia. We use a low 2mg dose of melatonin (most gummies pack 5-10mg, which is what causes the morning hangover) paired with 12 natural sleep herbs that calm your mind without knocking you out cold. You'll wake up rested, not foggy.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="90ff7235-c76b-4c50-a84d-0073f3628697" class="r-1f5eoa3" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="fa1509ec-7296-492b-910a-38788767c059" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R7b32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-f4vl9s"><div data-rid="9f3650fc-a352-44b9-828f-dceb0f13bcf3" class="r-spd8ep alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Is Rejuvia habit-forming? Will I become dependent on it?</p></span></div><div data-rid="06a96d3a-7ccc-4077-88e1-612b2bc3c8fd" class="r-kfj229" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-vmflic" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R7b32:"><div data-rid="72b0135a-39c9-4666-9b1d-18c010a90a4a" class="r-z25s0"><div data-rid="5f81f682-09b4-4bf6-871b-1b8a5aa8449e" class="r-1qgfk6n alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Not at all. Rejuvia is non-habit-forming, and you can use it every night or only when you need it. Most of our customers use it nightly as part of their wind-down routine because they love how they feel, not because they have to. Plenty of customers also use it 3-4 nights a week or only when travel and stress throw off their sleep.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="fa1c6061-1493-437f-8d13-24837f5b61ac" class="r-xzkqxu" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="93730976-45b3-4186-9af2-927a369a989a" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R9b32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-14wnv1k"><div data-rid="1692e044-489a-44a8-8667-fd5b47c79532" class="r-11jo0dd alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What are the ingredients in Rejuvia?</p></span></div><div data-rid="10c70107-3718-46d6-86b0-2f90191ce84e" class="r-h4mab2" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%"